'''Rikki Fleming''' (born 29 December 1946) is a Scottish former [[association football|footballer]], who played for [[Ayr United F.C.|Ayr United]], [[Hibernian F.C.|Hibernian]] and [[Berwick Rangers F.C.|Berwick Rangers]] in the [[Scottish Football League]].

